  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="container">
        <h1>What To Eat Next</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Astrological Guidance for the Present Moment</p>
        <p class="date">Current Time: {formattedDate}</p>
      </div>
    </header>
    
    <main class="container">
      <section class="page-links">
        <div class="cards-grid">
          <a href="/astro/current-chart" class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">‚òâ</div>
            <h3>View the Chart of the Moment</h3>
            <p>
              Explore the current planetary positions and elemental balance
              for this exact moment in time.
            </p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/astro/diet" class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">üçΩÔ∏è</div>
            <h3>Get Personalized Food Recommendations</h3>
            <p>
              Receive tailored dietary suggestions based on the current
              astrological influences.
            </p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="about">
        <h2>About This Moment</h2>
        <p>
          All calculations and recommendations are based on the exact
          planetary positions and astrological influences at the current time.
          The data is updated in real-time to provide the most accurate
          insights for this moment.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
      <div class="container">
        <p>
          Astrological calculations for the present moment | 
          What To Eat Next
        </p>
      </div>
